Author: Titan1x77

Name: de_peekaboo_v1

Release notes: V1 is the first release canadite for this map. Bot nav has been packed in the bsp. HDR enabled.

Type: Bomb/Diffuse; 64 spawns, 8 vs.8 is ideal for this map.

Description: Bails of hay protect you from fall damage / Hidden buttons in the underground area (they open walls) / Teleporters and jump pads.

Build notes: 
Started off as a gungame map, evolved into a small bomb defusal map.
Thanks to By Karatek√§fer for the great skybox texture. 
Thanks to Nipper for the hay texture.
Thanks to Chizbone for tuning the bot nav ( i made a change to spawn area and bots get hung up on them rarely *my fault*)

Enjoy!
